Package com.restfb.webhook

Class AbstractWebhookChangeListener

java.lang.Object
com.restfb.webhook.AbstractWebhookChangeListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
WebhookChangeListener
public abstract class AbstractWebhookChangeListener
extends Object
implements WebhookChangeListener
abstract class as base for custom webhook change listener, with this abstract class it is possible to implement only a subset of the need methods and ignore the other ones.
